Mirror Horror game. How to play.
the aim of this game is to kill all red enemy with a blue gun.
You have to move the ball with your cursour keys.
You can change mirror angle by place your self in the mirror and press <space bar> to change angel.
You can also change gun point by place your self in the gun and press <spave bar>.
you can pick up mirror with <0>.
you can place mirrors you picked up with <1>.
to fire gun, hit <return>.
Good luck!
